Subject: Specify the sort order of tg summary.

The --sort option now has more features:

  --sort=alphabetical   Sort the branches alphabetically.  This was
                        the old behaviour, and is still the default.

  --sort=topological    Do a dependency sort.
  --sort                Same as --sort=topological.

Use '--sort -t' to list the branch names, one per line.

Signed-off-by: Per Cederqvist <ceder@lysator.liu.se>
